                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8821" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1353</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1963 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">逆市而行觅商机，负商誉内涵引深思：康达新材收购赛英科技案例启示</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Seeking Business Opportunities Against the Market Trends Prompts Deep Reflection on the Information Content of Negative Goodwill: Insights from the Acquisition of Sine Technology by Kanda New Materials</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">张姗姗，张力予，鲍垚锦</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">北京交通大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">康达新材料（集团）股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">化学工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">15 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">企业并购；负商誉；公允价值</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Enterprise merger and acquisition; Negative goodwill; Fair value</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">非同一控制下的市场化并购会产生合并商誉，其正负取决于合并成本与被收购方可辨认净资产公允价值的差额。近五年来，我国资本市场每年都会发生千余起企业并购案，但其中99%的并购都会形成正商誉，这使得负商誉仿佛笼罩上了一层神秘的面纱。本案例选取深交所上市公司康达新材为研究对象，以购买方的视角展现了其因收购赛英科技而获得高额负商誉的过程，使学生了解负商誉产生的情境，掌握负商誉的计算过程、会计处理及其对企业业绩的影响，引导学生思考负商誉的内涵和本质、公允价值计量与负商誉的关系、以及负商誉现行会计处理的合理性等问题。本案例提供了一个深入了解和研究负商誉的珍贵机会，为企业披露负商誉信息以及报表使用者理解负商誉的内涵提供了经验和启示，为准则制定机构修订企业合并会计准则提供了借鉴和参考。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">In market-driven acquisitions not under common control, goodwill arises, with its positive or negative value determined by the difference between the acquisition cost and the fair value of identifiable net assets of the acquired entity. In the past five years, China’s capital market has witnessed over a thousand corporate mergers and acquisitions annually, with 99% resulting in positive goodwill, shrouding negative goodwill in mystery. This case study focuses on Kangda New Material, a company listed on the Shenzhen Stock Exchange, to illustrate the process of acquiring significant negative goodwill through the acquisition of Sine Technology from the acquirer’s perspective. It aims to familiarize students with the context of negative goodwill formation, make them understand the calculation process, accounting treatment, and the impact of negative goodwill on short-term and long-term performance of companies. It also encourages students to contemplate the essence of negative goodwill, fair value measurement and its the relationship with negative goodwill, and the reasonableness of current accounting treatments. This case study provides a valuable opportunity for in-depth understanding and research on negative goodwill, offering experience and insights for companies disclosing negative goodwill information and stakeholders comprehending its implications, and serving as a reference for standard-setting bodies revising accounting standards for corporate mergers.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,博士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《会计学》、《高级财务会计》、《资产评估》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">负商誉的基本概念；负商誉的形成原因；负商誉的确认和计量；负商誉的本质内涵；负商誉会计处理的合理性；资产评估方法</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-11</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
